Name: ZOOM_CAMERA_CONTROL_WIDTH
TextValue: Percentage of the screen used for camera zoom

Name: SOUND_LISTENER_OFFSET
TextValue: Fake immersion by moving 3D sound listener closer to player(or ground) position instead of actual camera position. 100 = player pos, 0 = camera.

Name: THREAT_DISTANCE_NORMAL
TextValue: The distance before enemies are considered threats.

Name: THREAT_THRESHOLD_NORMAL
TextValue: The sum of threat needed to reach a higher level of threat. Used to affect music.
